            text: "Spiritually, allowing evil to flourish when you have the power and duty to stop it is a severe Adharma. If Arjuna lets them kill him, Duryodhana rules the earth unchecked. Arjuna's 'compassion' for his family would result in the suffering of millions of innocent citizens.",
