          text: "This is the textbook definition of 'Spiritual Bypassing'—using spiritual concepts (like 'peace' or 'higher intelligence') to avoid dealing with unresolved psychological issues, difficult boundaries, or necessary conflicts. Arjuna is trying to spiritually bypass the Kurukshetra war.",
