          text: "You set your alarm for 5 AM to work out. You actively *want* to be fit. But at 5 AM, you hit snooze and sleep for two more hours, feeling terrible about it. You broke your diet 'even unwillingly.' We live this verse every single day. We are constantly baffled by our own self-sabotage.",
