          title: "Reflective Question",
          text: "Which of these four currencies (Wealth, Discipline, Meditation, or Deep Study) am I most naturally equipped to offer right now, and how can I formalize that offering with a 'strict vow' (Saṃśita-vratāḥ) today?",
