            title: "The Interruption of the Default Mode",
            text: "When you focus entirely on the mechanics of inhalation and exhalation, rumination and obsessive thinking (the Default Mode Network) are forcibly shut down. The breath becomes an anchor that drags the wandering mind back into the absolute present moment.",
