            title: "Action as the Only Vehicle",
            text: "Psychologically, people often wait for an 'epiphany' to strike them while they sit passively, hoping it will cure their depression or confusion. This verse shatters that passive hope. Epiphanies do not cure; action cures. Every valid psychological or spiritual breakthrough is 'Karma-jān'—born from the friction of actively participating in your own recovery.",
