            title: "The Totality of the Shift",
            text: "A candle only illuminates a small room, but the sun (Āditya) illuminates the entire hemisphere simultaneously. When the 'ignorance' is finally destroyed, the resulting clarity is not partial or fragmented. It is an overwhelming, totalizing paradigm shift that instantly re-contextualizes everything in the universe.",
